GRID-ITEM
1 grid-area :It  is used to achieve the functionalities of grid-row-start and grid-row-end.
2 grid-row  :It specifies the grid itemâ€™s name

GRID-CONTAINER
1 Grid-template-columns:It define the number of column.
2 Grid-template-row: It define the height of each row.
